HBA 9400-8i8e Tri-Mode Storage Adapter





























































Broadcom
































 Products  Storage Adapters, Controllers, and ICs  SAS/SATA/NVMe Host Bus Adapters  HBA 9400-8i8e Tri-Mode Storage Adapter


Print
Share Page

















										Contact Sales








										Contact Sales






xClose












Request Info





xClose














										  	HBA 9400-8i8e Tri-Mode Storage Adapter

										  	Provide internal and external storage to high-performance connectivity applications






Currently Viewing:


Overview

Overview


Specifications


Documentation


Downloads









Overview





Specifications





Documentation





Downloads






Overview






















Designed for large-scale external storage enclosures and internal storage, the 9400-8i8e Tri-Mode Storage Adapter is ideal for increased connectivity and maximum performance for data center flexibility.
With increased  bandwidth and IOPS performance compared to previous generations, the 9400-8i8e adapter delivers the performance and scalability needed by critical applications.

Connects up to 1024 SAS/SATA devices; and up 24 (internal only) NVMe* devices per controller
Provides maximum connectivity and performance for high-end servers and applications
Support critical applications with the bandwidth of PCIe® 3.1 connectivity
Ideal for connecting large-scale external storage enclosures and internal storage

* x2 and 24 max NVMe drive support available at a later release. 






