Product
Manufacturer Part #
What's in the Box




HBA 9400-8i8e
05-50031-02
9400-8ie HBA, Low Profile Bracket, Getting Started Guide



 




Specification
Value





Lifecycle
Active



Host Bus Type
x8 lane PCI Express® 3.1



Physical Dimensions
6.600" x 2.712"



Devices Supported
SAS/SATA: 1024; NVMe: 24



External Connectors
2 Mini-SAS HD SFF8644



Internal Connectors
2 Mini-SAS HD SFF8643



Internal Ports
8



Operating Temperature
10° to 55° C



Operating Voltage (V)
+12V +/-8%, 3.3V +/-9%



OS Support
Microsoft Windows, Linux, VMware.



PCI Power
Typical Power: 12.39W



Cable Support
Passive Copper, Active Copper (ext), Active Optical (ext)



I/O Controller
SAS3516



MTBF
 > 4,500,000 hours at 40° C



Operating Humidity
20% to 80% Non-condensing



Brackets
Full height and low profile



Regulatory Certifications
Australia/New Zealand (AS/NZS CISPR 22), Canada (ICES -003, Class B), Europe (EN55022/EN55024), Japan (VCCI V-3), Korea (RRA no 2013-24 & 25), RoHS, Safety: EN60950, Taiwan (CNS 13438), USA (FCC 47 CFR part 15 Subpart B, class B), WEEE



Warranty
3 years, free technical support, advanced replacement option at broadcom.com/support/warranty/internal-raid-hba



Data Transfer Rates
12Gb/s SAS-3 Compliant



Management Software
LSI Storage Authority (LSA), StorCLI, Unified StorLib








